      <title>科恩接受严厉质询 特朗普辩护获助力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/trump-defense-gets-boost-from-aggressive-cohen-cross-examination</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，唐纳德·特朗普在封口费审判中的律师在证人席上盘问了迈克尔·科恩几个小时，指责他的证词中可能存在不一致之处，以及他有据可查的宣誓撒谎的历史。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/trump-defense-gets-boost-from-aggressive-cohen-cross-examination</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 20:40:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
